{"tid":2036373,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"如果何鴻燊故事係TVB拍劇 劇情應該點寫好？","createTime":"2020-05-26T12:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T12:30:29.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d352f956d5417cb02eb8150407eee6f8dd114951","tid":2036373,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"結局一定係二奶三奶四奶一齊一邊BBQ 一邊分身家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他29集點寫好？"},{"pid":"f533a4f2cac923dc05918ef7bcc0dccdb54371f5","tid":2036373,"uid":340106,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:10:16.000Z","msg":"唔撚睇tvb，完"},{"pid":"268fba2b5cb85cf377e30f38f9e728d65072058a","tid":2036373,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:10:57.000Z","msg":"羅兆輝日前爆富豪和女星的性史，鬧得滿城風雨，賭王前晚出席灣仔君悅酒店一個活動時，「雀躍地」大談羅兆輝口中另一個富豪的秘聞，還發表「鹹濕可治風濕」的理論。<br />\n<br />\n由協康會主辦的「第十一屆全港名廚精英大滙演」，前晚於灣仔君悅酒店舉行。大會邀請特首夫人董趙洪娉出席主持，而城中名人包括何鴻燊與二姨太藍瓊纓、郭炳湘夫人、陳方安生胞弟方曼生等均有到場品嘗美食。<br />\n<br />\n邊講邊笑甚興奮<br />\n<br />\n賭王何鴻燊、二姨太藍瓊纓、兒子何猷龍及女兒何超蕸前晚亦有出席。賭王除即席試食外，更笑談有關羅兆輝爆富豪性史的報道，賭王談及這些富豪性史時，顯得非常雀躍，還發表「鹹濕可治風濕」的理論，妙趣橫生，以下是賭王談富豪性史的內容：<br />\n<br />\n記：記者 何：何鴻燊<br />\n<br />\n記：有報道指富豪打針催谷噃？<br />\n何（狂笑）：需唔需要呀！我冇聽過，咁水皮。<br />\n記：報道指係你啲老友。<br />\n何：唔係嘛，咁丟架！<br />\n記者告知何鴻燊報道中暗喻的某富豪，賭王聞言反應甚大說：「嘩，唔好嚇我！佢幾多歲呀？（記者即告之賭王）哦，佢有好多girlfriend（女朋友）！」<br />\n記：有否教他「有心有力」的心得呢？<br />\n何（開懷地笑）：呢啲搵女人教啦！佢啲girlfriend好後生，級數好犀利，全部十九至二十一歲！<br />\n<br />\n首次聽「起雙飛」<br />\n記：報道更指他愛「起雙飛」。<br />\n何（眉飛色舞）：咁犀利！今晚我第一次聽。<br />\n記：報道亦說他不愛用安全套。<br />\n何（亢奮地說）：唔好笑死我啦！<br />\n記：會否向他求證？<br />\n何：唔會。我會教佢兩道板斧。我同你哋講，一個人想風濕好番，鹹濕啲就得，我會教佢！<br />\n記：賭王有風濕嗎？<br />\n何（自豪地說）：我一滴都冇！"},{"pid":"3fa6bcc9a86077b15a9dc8a3fd9a35b64576d653","tid":2036373,"uid":21716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"重播賭城大亨得啦!"},{"pid":"9e68f1fe7c6da5af04573a7857268721c5be36f3","tid":2036373,"uid":178109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"幾房人互相打巴掌打足29集，最後BBQ大結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c70342f30a722b1d975960670d9254b6a7eb978","tid":2036373,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e68f1fe7c6da5af04573a7857268721c5be36f3","tid":2036373,"uid":178109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"幾房人互相打巴掌打足29集，最後BBQ大結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中間燊哥機械人換精密零件要加D五毛特效先得架喔<br />\n咪變超科幻動作片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f2f193f061f155c5152389a956eaf611a629ff","tid":2036373,"uid":165106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d352f956d5417cb02eb8150407eee6f8dd114951","tid":2036373,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"結局一定係二奶三奶四奶一齊一邊BBQ 一邊分身家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他29集點寫好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:30:29.0